OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA largely
OL,6,Fcloudy start to the evening, but an
OL,7,Fincreasing chance of a few clearer
OL,8,Fspells developing as the night goes
OL,9,Fon. Remaining on the breezy side,
OL,10,Fespecially along the coasts. Dry
OL,11,Fovernight and mild.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FStaying dry with variable
OL,14,Famounts of cloud during Monday
OL,15,Fmorning. However, increasing amounts
OL,16,Fof sunshine are likely to develop into
OL,17,Fthe afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
